mendesak, kan?

578
00:32:02,254 --> 00:32:04,256
Ya, perlu, Sayang.

579
00:32:04,798 --> 00:32:08,344
Kita tak bisa memperlakukan doa
seperti ban serep

580
00:32:08,427 --> 00:32:11,472
